Package jalse.misc

This package is for shared utilities across all other packages.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Identifiable
    This is for anything that should be uniquely identifiable within JALSE.
    ProxyCache.ProxyFactory
    Proxy type validator and ProxyCache.CacheHandler creation factory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIdentifiable
    This is an abstract implementation of Identifiable.
    JALSEExceptions
    These are the suppliers for all the common specific exceptions JALSE throws.
    ProxyCache
    A type validating proxy cache where proxies of different types can be associated to an owner.
    ProxyCache.CacheHandler
    An abstract InvocationHandler implementation that references a WeakReference owner.

Package jalse.misc Description

This package is for shared utilities across all other packages.
